rows.label: qst702007_msg0003
rows.name: No, this is Aletta. A province of Iira.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0009
rows.name: I'm so glad you're all right!

rows.label: qst702007_msg0012
rows.name: I'm so... *sniff* glad we got to help...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0014
rows.name:
Adel-sama.
Thank you for the kindness you have
shown me and my family.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0015
rows.name:
Nonsense.
I'm terribly sorry about your wife.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0017
rows.name: But at least I still have my children.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0018
rows.name:
They're more than I would have had
without your help.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0019
rows.name:
Together, we'll take care of each other
and honor Nelly's memory.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0020
rows.name:
Excellent.
Just take it easy. You need to give
yourself time to grieve, too.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0021
rows.name:
You too, Adel-sama. I know you're
the type to put your life on the line for
others, but do take care of yourself.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0023
rows.name:
He's got all of us here doing his
work for him. I'd say he'll be taking
it plenty easy.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0027
rows.name:
We'll be living here from now,
so come play sometime!

rows.label: qst702007_msg0028
rows.name:
Sure thing, Kai. See you, Kei.
Stay out of trouble, now!
